textBeforeTable: Sports Registration begins Dec-18-2015 to Dec-20-2015, Sun, Fri, Sat, 6 - 10pm AL: Wading Pool Attendant & SFA/CPR-C  (14yrs and over) The Wading Pool Attendant award is designed to provide lifesavers the knowledge and skill to supervise a Wading Pool. In Ontario, a wading pool is a pool of water less than 0.75 metres (2 feet, 6 inches) in depth. This course includes Standard First Aid with CPR-C (unless otherwise noted). If you withdraw from a program 10 days or less from the course start date, a 50% refund is provided. No refunds are given for classes or programs that you miss. 100% attendance and active participation are mandatory! AL: Wading Pool Attendant (WPA) Oct-31-2014
